HEADWORD: Dynactinometer
<hw>Dy*nac`ti*nom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
power + E. <ets>actinometer</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument for
measuring the intensity of the photogenic (light-producing) rays, and
computing the power of object glasses.</def>⟦br⟧
